## 8. Atmospheric Relay Envelope

A newly defined operational layer.

### Concept:

The aircraft uses the atmosphere itself as part of the communication system.

### Mechanisms:

* Tropospheric signal bounce modeling
* Humidity-based refraction correction
* Altitude-adjusted transmission shaping

### Result:

* Extended communication reach beyond line-of-sight limits
* Stabilized signal behavior in turbulent conditions

